Fast-rising Nigerian music star, Rema who caught the attention of music lovers with his catchy EP, “Rema” has released the video for “Dumebi” that was the highlight of the EP. The teen sensation gives us a wistful and lovestruck image of himself in the new video of the melodic-shoulder shaker track as he tries to catch the attention of his love interest. He is, however, the other guy as he and four friends enjoy a good time on a camping trip that includes a girl he’s in love with. Her boyfriend is also on the trip hence he is unable to express his love for her. Check on the video below: 